{"tid":2014552,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人去過澳門考車牌？","createTime":"2020-05-13T06:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T23:53:36.000Z","uid":4655,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"85d73c6e64cc28a4d05398f0bf404fdca719439c","tid":2014552,"uid":4655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:08:29.000Z","msg":"有冇人試過？ 我本身有1，2牌，但如果去澳門考26 有冇得諗？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳門筆試難唔難？駛唔駛上晒堂去考定係自修搞掂？<br />\n<br />\n我諗過轉個香港1，2牌過去，唔駛考筆試，但睇過要二千蚊唔太化算。<br />\n<br />\n利申： 有馬交身分證，想去考因為勝在有650cc ，第日去外國可直接換大cc 牌（香港個廢牌去到人地度可能揸唔到大cc車）<br />\n<br />\n加上排期三個月有得考。加上冇P牌制度（其實有P)但P 牌其實係正式牌。可以即刻轉返香港3號牌。"},{"pid":"d7e78d07a7a0d37928439a77f7dd2fcafc17416f","tid":2014552,"uid":26635,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:20:08.000Z","msg":"排期考試有鳩排你排 考個牌分分鐘都要等一年"},{"pid":"2318e1cf17369b9833a3c57fbb9cc23f21aa780c","tid":2014552,"uid":99016,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:41:41.000Z","msg":"香港有得考又唔考<br />\n<br />\n返大陸考，俾錢搞掂<br />\n再返香港轉返港牌<br />\n<br />\n利申：鳩up"},{"pid":"51f30c491dd40e99d087fdfa3dbcf5f08a19ba72","tid":2014552,"uid":4655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7e78d07a7a0d37928439a77f7dd2fcafc17416f","tid":2014552,"uid":26635,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:20:08.000Z","msg":"排期考試有鳩排你排 考個牌分分鐘都要等一年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:42:31.000Z","msg":"三個月<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K2Y2J3N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK2Y2J3N.png&h=3260015f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92fa43fc7d93e9c70787d718a89c124e791d29c7","tid":2014552,"uid":4655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2318e1cf17369b9833a3c57fbb9cc23f21aa780c","tid":2014552,"uid":99016,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:41:41.000Z","msg":"香港有得考又唔考<br />\n<br />\n返大陸考，俾錢搞掂<br />\n再返香港轉返港牌<br />\n<br />\n利申：鳩up"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:46:18.000Z","msg":"香港考慘過做乞丐，排個期都要成年，教車師傅寸過馬撚。<br />\n<br />\n澳門我就咁睇相對快，出黎又係正式牌，我又有路面經驗。邊度考一樣。同埋可以用消費券，淨係比政府錢已經搞掂（2000左右）。不過係要去上足廿五堂先比考。"},{"pid":"559cfbd536c84024a01fa1c73cbce9b27fc49d15","tid":2014552,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:50:40.000Z","msg":"有兩邊身份證，一定係澳門考好"},{"pid":"2d5d7fb9a4b6cb0052976c12af637d283828e3da","tid":2014552,"uid":4655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"559cfbd536c84024a01fa1c73cbce9b27fc49d15","tid":2014552,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:50:40.000Z","msg":"有兩邊身份證，一定係澳門考好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:53:20.000Z","msg":"巴打係馬交人？"},{"pid":"313ad0110a5e16ec78b8939e445c1b43480b3838","tid":2014552,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d5d7fb9a4b6cb0052976c12af637d283828e3da","tid":2014552,"uid":4655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"559cfbd536c84024a01fa1c73cbce9b27fc49d15","tid":2014552,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:50:40.000Z","msg":"有兩邊身份證，一定係澳門考好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:53:20.000Z","msg":"巴打係馬交人？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:56:46.000Z","msg":"大學roommate係馬交人<br />\n佢喺澳門考<br />\n話反正可以直接換返香港，而香港排條龍又長，學車又貴，根本冇著數"},{"pid":"a8f5bc6eca4476780aad09ba29e418fd08e8cc6a","tid":2014552,"uid":4655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"313ad0110a5e16ec78b8939e445c1b43480b3838","tid":2014552,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d5d7fb9a4b6cb0052976c12af637d283828e3da","tid":2014552,"uid":4655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"559cfbd536c84024a01fa1c73cbce9b27fc49d15","tid":2014552,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:50:40.000Z","msg":"有兩邊身份證，一定係澳門考好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:53:20.000Z","msg":"巴打係馬交人？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:56:46.000Z","msg":"大學roommate係馬交人<br />\n佢喺澳門考<br />\n話反正可以直接換返香港，而香港排條龍又長，學車又貴，根本冇著